body:
### Welcome to Mayela Delatorre's Blog.

This is my first blog using the automatic generator on GitHub. What a fantastic tool to learn how to github. Love it thanks so much Sean for the outstanding resources you refer us too!!

### Classes currently enrolled in at Oregon State Ecampus
1. CS325 Analysis of Algorithms 
2. CS361 Software Engineering I
3. CS494 Web Development 
4. CS311 Operating Systems I

### About Me
As a mother of a wonderful 11 year old son, he is what motivates me to continue in Computer Science. I love innovation and developing programs that will help my son and his generation enjoy computer science and technology. I plan on doing an internship this coming summer and look forward to experiencing the real on the job coding.
